<h2>How do I install Factlink in my browser?</h2>

<p>When you are a Google Chrome user you can install our <a href="help/chrome-extension">Chrome Extension</a>. Once installed, simply annotate the text you want and click the extension. We have created also a <a href="help/chrome-extension">video</a> so you can watch how easy it is to create a Factlink.</p>

<p>For everyone else we made a special bookmarklet wich you can easily drag to your bookmarks bar. Simply click on it and annotate the text you want. The Factlink menu appears and you can give your opinion about the statement.</p>

<h2>How do I follow someone?</h2>
<p>
We think it’s better to follow specific topics from persons instead of following persons. That is the reason why you can’t follow a person. You can follow a channel from someone by adding their channel to your own channel list.
</p>


<h2>How do I get authority?</h2>
<p>
Authority is gained by creating relevant and interesting Factlinks. When people interact more with your Factlinks you gain more authority.
</p>
